## 7. MODEL PATTERN

### 7.1 MongoDB Model
```java
package com.{COMPANY_NAME}.{service}.model;

@Getter
@Setter
@NoArgsConstructor
@Document(collection = "{entity}")
public class {Entity}Model {
    
    @Id
    private String {entity}Id;
    
    private String field;
    private Boolean isActive;
    private Instant createdOn;
    private String createdBy;
    private Instant lastModifiedOn;
    private String lastModifiedBy;
}
```

### 7.2 JPA/PostgreSQL Model
```java
package com.{COMPANY_NAME}.{service}.model;

@Getter
@Setter
@NoArgsConstructor
@Entity
@Table(name = "{entity}", schema = "public")
@TypeDef(name = "jsonb", typeClass = JsonBinaryType.class)
public class {Entity}Model implements Serializable {
    
    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
    
    @Id
    @Column(name = "{entity}_id")
    private String {entity}Id;
    
    @Column(name = "field_name")
    private String fieldName;
    
    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(name = "status", columnDefinition = "{entity}_status")
    @Type(type = "pgenum")
    private Status status;
    
    @Type(type = "jsonb")
    @Column(name = "extension", columnDefinition = "jsonb")
    private Map<String, Object> extension;
    
    @Column(name = "created_on")
    private Instant createdOn;
    
    @Column(name = "created_by")
    private String createdBy;
    
    @Column(name = "last_modified_on")
    private Instant lastModifiedOn;
    
    @Column(name = "last_modified_by")
    private String lastModifiedBy;
}
```

### 7.3 Value Object (VO)
```java
package com.{COMPANY_NAME}.{service}.vo;

@Getter
@Setter
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
public class {Entity} {
    
    private String {entity}Id;
    
    @NotBlank(message = "Field is required")
    private String field;
    
    private Boolean isActive;
    private Instant createdOn;
    private String createdBy;
    private Instant lastModifiedOn;
    private String lastModifiedBy;
    
    // For nested objects, use specific VOs
    private List<RelatedVO> relatedItems;
    
    // For flexible data, use Map
    private Map<String, Object> extension;
}
```

