log.info("{ClassName}::{methodName}: End - Successfully completed");
log.error("{ClassName}::{methodName}: Error - ", exception);
log.debug("{ClassName}::{methodName}: Debug info - {}", data);
```

### 10.2 Use @Slf4j from Lombok
```java
@Slf4j
@Service
public class MyServiceImpl implements MyService {
    // log is automatically available
}
```

