## 12. COMMON ANNOTATIONS

### 12.1 Class Level
- `@Service` - Service implementations
- `@Repository` - Repository interfaces
- `@RestController` - REST controllers
- `@ControllerAdvice` - Exception handlers
- `@Component` - Generic beans
- `@Slf4j` - Logging
- `@RefreshScope` - Config refresh support
- `@Getter`, `@Setter`, `@NoArgsConstructor` - Lombok

### 12.2 Method Level
- `@Override` - Interface method implementations
- `@Transactional` - Transaction management
- `@Scheduled` - Scheduled tasks
- `@Async` - Async execution

### 12.3 Field Level
- `@Autowired` - Dependency injection
- `@Value("${property.name}")` - Property injection
- `@Valid` - Validation
- `@NotBlank`, `@NotNull` - Validation constraints

---

## 13. NAMING CONVENTIONS

### 13.1 Classes
- Controller: `{Entity}Controller`, `{Entity}ControllerImpl`
- Service: `{Entity}Service`, `{Entity}ServiceImpl`
- Repository: `{Entity}Repository`
- Model: `{Entity}Model`
- VO: `{Entity}` (without suffix) or `{Entity}VO`
- Exception: `{Entity}Exception`, `{Entity}NotFoundException`

### 13.2 Methods
- Get: `get{Entity}ById`, `getAll{Entity}s`
- Create: `create{Entity}`, `save{Entity}`
- Update: `update{Entity}`, `update{Entity}Parameters`
- Delete: `delete{Entity}`, `remove{Entity}`
- Search: `search{Entity}s`, `searchByParameters`
- Link/Tag: `link{X}To{Y}`, `tag{X}To{Y}`

### 13.3 Variables
- Use camelCase
- Repository: `{entity}Repository`
- Service: `{entity}Service`
- Model: `{entity}Model`
- List: `{entity}List` or `{entity}s`

